@ParametersAreNonnullByDefault

Package com.gl.vn.me.ko.sample.instrumentation.example.proxy

Contains sample classes for proxies.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BigDecimalProxyFactoryExampleB
    The class provides an ability to create a CGLib-proxy (enhanced object) of type BigDecimal that can intercept invocation of any non-final and non-private method of class BigDecimal and perform additional actions (see MethodInterceptorExampleB.intercept(Object, Method, Object[], MethodProxy)).
    InvocationHandlerExampleC
    This class is an invocation handler that is used by MapProxyFactoryExampleC to create Java-proxy objects.
    MapProxyFactoryExampleC
    The class provides an ability to create a Java-proxy object of type Map that can intercept invocation of any method of interface Map and perform additional actions (see InvocationHandlerExampleC.invoke(Object, Method, Object[])).
    MethodInterceptorExampleB
    This class is a method interceptor that is used by BigDecimalProxyFactoryExampleB to create CGLib-proxy objects.
